      "severity": "critical",
      "description": "Credit card input fields use placeholder text as labels ('Card number', 'MM/YY', 'CVV'). When users start typing, the label disappears. This also breaks for screen reader users.",
      "fixSuggestion": "Add visible labels above or beside each input field using the label element with for attribute.",
